content: I changed my review from 5 to 3 stars. The last update, 3.21.1.8 from 3.20.1.8, made the Nest Thermostat device interface in Home worse. It did have four control shortcuts in a bar under the graphic temperature "dial": Mode, Temperature Presets, Hold, and Fan.
